title: 5 Cheyne Walk
text:
5 Cheyne Walk is a Grade II* listed house on <a href="Cheyne%20Walk">Cheyne Walk</a>, Chelsea, London, built in 1718.
The miser <a href="John%20Camden%20Neild">John Camden Neild</a> lived there from 1814 until his death in 1852.
5 Cheyne Walk is now the residence of the Cypriot High Commissioner to the UK.
